video_title: Be the main character in your life story! #maincharacterenergy #kerrywashington #jayshetty
transcript:
I always felt like I was the co-star in
somebody else's story whether it's at
work or at home or whatever that writing
this Memoir was a little bit about like
I got that missing puzzle piece that
helped me put myself at the center of my
story and then I was like I want to do
the work to write that I want to do the
work to know what it feels like to
Center myself so that I can make sure
that in this lifetime I'm living my
story and not chasing somebody else's
